{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# to [[assure]], to [[ensure]], to [[make sure]]\n# to do; to [[take care of]]; to [[carry out]]; to be [[in charge of]]\n#: {{ux|fr|Des bénévoles '''assurent''' le nettoyage des lieux.|Volunteers '''take care of''' the cleaning of the premises.}}\n# to [[insure]], to give [[insurance]] to\n# {{lb|fr|climbing}} to [[belay]]\n\n====Usage notes====\n'''S'assurer que''', in the sense of \"make sure,\" takes the indicative mood: ''Assurez-vous que la porte est bien fermée.'' [http://bdl.oqlf.gouv.qc.ca/bdl/gabarit_bdl.asp?id=4031] The subjunctive is seen at times (''Assurez-vous que la porte soit bien fermée''), especially where the connotation is that the listener should check and then do the thing if it is not already done, but is generally [[Appendix:Glossary#proscribed|proscribed]].\n\n====Conjugation====\n{{fr-conj-auto}}\n\n====Derived terms====\n* {{l|fr|assurer ses arrières}}\n\n====Related terms====\n* {{l|fr|assurance}}\n* {{l|fr|assureur}}\n\n====Descendants====\n* {{desc|da|assurere|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ro|asigura|bor=1|qq=partial calque}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":true,"impers":false}],"trans":["to insure","to assure, to ensure, to make sure","to do","to take care of","to carry out","to be in charge of","to insure, to give insurance to","to belay"],"group":1,"conj":[{"mod":"indc","tenses":[{"tense":"pres","forms":[["j'assur","e"],["tu assur","es"],["il assur","e"],["nous assur","ons"],["vous assur","ez"],["ils assur","ent"]]},{"tense":"pass-c","forms":[["j'ai assur","é"],["tu as assur","é"],["il a assur","é"],["nous avons assur","é"],["vous avez assur","é"],["ils ont assur","é"]]},{"tense":"impf","forms":[["j'assur","ais"],["tu assur","ais"],["il assur","ait"],["nous assur","ions"],["vous assur","iez"],["ils assur","aient"]]},{"tense":"pqpf","forms":[["j'avais assur","é"],["tu avais assur","é"],["il avait assur","é"],["nous avions assur","é"],["vous aviez assur","é